  <brief_title>Efficacy of the ATP Switch Automatic Programming in Implantable Cardioverter Defibrillator (ICD) and Cardiac Resynchronization Therapy Defibrillator (CRT-D) Implanted Patients</brief_title>
  <acronym>ASAP</acronym>
  <official_title>Efficacy of the ATP Switch Automatic Programming in ICD and CRT-D Implanted Patients</official_title>
