  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Primary objective is to assess the efficacy of the new ATP Autoswitch function in simple,
      dual or triple chamber ICD.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The efficacy rate of the ATP Auto-switch function, defined as the % of VT episodes
      successfully reduced, will be compared with 85%.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
